OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F163A1775563865
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G2/3
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sun 12 Apr to Tue 21 AprFIt
OL,6,Fwill likely remain rather changeable
OL,7,Fduring the first part of this period
OL,8,Fwith showers or occasional longer
OL,9,Fspells of rain affecting many areas.
OL,10,FWhether this takes the form of
OL,11,Fsuccessive weather systems pushing in
OL,12,Ffrom the Atlantic or a more slowly
OL,13,Fevolving weather pattern remains
OL,14,Frather unclear. There may also be some
OL,15,Fdrier and brighter interludes and when
OL,16,Fwinds are light, it should feel quite
OL,17,Fwarm, despite temperatures most likely
OL,18,Fbeing close to normal for most. Later
OL,19,Fin the month more blocked weather
OL,20,Fpatterns become more likely, with high
OL,21,Fpressure in the vicinity of the UK.
OL,22,FThis increases the probability of more
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,23,Fsettled weather, especially in the
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
OL,24,Fnorth but there may still be periods
OL,25,Fof rain or showers, especially in the
OL,26,Fsouth.
FL,164,160,301,260,100,100
PN,16303
SC,0003
CT,20,T
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F163A1775563865
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G3/3
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tue 21 Apr to Tue 5 May
OL,6,FHigh pressure will probably be the
OL,7,Fmost dominant pattern during this
OL,8,Fperiod with a good deal of dry weather
OL,9,Facross the UK as whole. Some unsettled
OL,10,Finterludes could develop at times, but
OL,11,Foverall rainfall amounts are expected
OL,12,Fto be below average. Temperatures will
OL,13,Fprobably be near to or slightly above
OL,14,Fnormal, although some cold nights are
OL,15,Fstill possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,164,160,301,260,100,100
